snippet.title: The EVE Online Experience - Play For Free (Trailer)
snippet.description:
EVE Online is the space, sandbox MMORPG that goes beyond anything you've experienced before. Every decision counts. Every journey is unique. Every pilot has a different tale. 
 
Play for free: http://www.eveonline.com 
 
Subscribe to our channel https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCwF3VyalTHzL0L-GDlwtbRw
Join us on Facebook https://www.facebook.com/eveonline
 
Visit updates.eveonline.com for the latest updates, expansions, and player gatherings
